1. Created a directory called 0x03-sass_scss inside the alx-intermediate-frontend repository:
   mkdir -p alx-intermediate-frontend/0x03-sass_scss
   cd alx-intermediate-frontend/0x03-sass_scss

2. Installed Node Version Manager (NVM) to manage Node.js versions:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

3. Exited the terminal and reopened it to enable NVM.

4. Installed Node.js version 20.16 using NVM:
   nvm install 20.16
   nvm use 20.16

5. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 using npm:
   npm install sass@3.7.4

6. Verified the installation by checking the SASS version:
   npx sass --version
